snippet: A federal judge issued an injunction that blocks a law requiring abortion providers to have admitting privileges at nearby hospitals for another four months.
lead_paragraph: A federal judge issued an injunction that blocks a law requiring abortion providers to have admitting privileges at nearby hospitals for another four months.

headline.main: Requirement for Abortion Providers in Wisconsin Is Blocked by a Federal Judge
